snippet.title: Guitar Hero Warriors of Rock - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: It's nearly here! 24/09/2010 sees the release of Guitar Hero: Warriors of Rock! The 6th major release in the franchise. Check out the launch trailer and get ready to start your quest on Friday!
